  </nav>

  <div class="financial-quiz-container">
    <h2>ðŸ§  Student Financial Quiz (Complete All 10 Questions)</h2>
    
    <div class="quiz-intro">
      <p>You only need to answer 10 questions to complete the quiz!</p>
    </div>

    <form action="/submit-quiz" method="POST">

      <div class="question">
        <p>1. What is a key benefit of a savings account?</p>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="A"> <span>High-risk investing</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="B"> <span>Safe place to store money and earn interest</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="C"> <span>No limit on withdrawals</span></label>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <p>2. Which habit best supports budgeting success?</p>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="A"> <span>Spending first, saving later</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="B"> <span>Tracking expenses regularly</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="C"> <span>Relying on memory for monthly bills</span></label>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <p>3. What does "pay yourself first" mean?</p>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="A"> <span>Spend all income on bills</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="B"> <span>Save a portion of income before spending</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="C"> <span>Wait for sales to shop more</span></label>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <p>4. What is a fixed deposit account?</p>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="A"> <span>A flexible account with unlimited withdrawals</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="B"> <span>An account where money is locked in for a set period and earns higher interest</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="C"> <span>A type of loan from a bank</span></label>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <p>5. Which of these helps grow your savings fastest?</p>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="A"> <span>Using an account with compound interest</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="B"> <span>Keeping cash at home</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="C"> <span>Spending leftover money monthly</span></label>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <p>6. Why is it important to review your monthly transactions?</p>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="A"> <span>To increase your credit score</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="B"> <span>To get more money from the bank</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="C"> <span>To catch errors and monitor spending habits</span></label>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <p>7. What's a good reason to open a fixed deposit instead of a savings account?</p>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="A"> <span>You want unlimited withdrawals</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="B"> <span>You plan to withdraw daily</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="C"> <span>You want higher guaranteed interest for a set period</span></label>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <p>8. How can you avoid overspending?</p>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q8" value="A"> <span>Stick to a written or digital budget</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q8" value="B"> <span>Guess your expenses each month</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q8" value="C"> <span>Ignore sale items</span></label>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <p>9. What does compound interest mean?</p>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q9" value="A"> <span>Interest is only paid once a year</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q9" value="B"> <span>You pay interest to the bank</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q9" value="C"> <span>You earn interest on your savings and the interest it earns</span></label>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <p>10. What's a smart goal when saving money?</p>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q10" value="A"> <span>"Save $500 in 3 months for a laptop."</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q10" value="B"> <span>"I want to save more someday."</span></label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q10" value="C"> <span>"Spend all my allowance first."</span></label>
      </div>

      <div class="submit-section">
        <button type="submit">Submit Quiz</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
